they can drop some of their Welcome gas off at a secondary upstream point, s=
uch as Marshall.  But their Aberdeen contract needs to flow at either Aberde=
en or Warner on our system.  And if their capacity is stranded at Aberdeen o=
n the 1st, I am confident that they will be giving both of us a call. =20
=20
